  <summary date="2021-06-03T13:31:18Z" status="Introduced in House">Help Independent Tracks Succeed Act or the HITS Act

This bill permits taxpayers to treat as currently deductible expenses the cost of qualified sound recording productions not exceeding $150,000 in a taxable year. The bill defines qualified sound recording production as certain sound recordings produced and recorded in the United States.</summary>
